      "content": "but it doesnt feel like just mood stuff. its too consistent. like there are these tiny extra layers in the background of the tracks that wouldnt be there normally. if someone actually wanted to do this using audio modulation, what would that even look like technically? like what kind of frequencies would they use to mess with someone's head?",
